text = "Descend as deep as possible, then plant the flag to save your score.
Death or a flag destroyed by lava loses the run.

A/D — move or swing    Space — jump
W/S — shorten or lengthen the rope
Left mouse — throw selected item
Right mouse hold/release — grapple/detach
1/2/3 — select item    Esc — pause or back

Phone: left stick moves, right stick aims/throws, outer ring grapples."
